    "guideLearnDesc": "By completing this guide, you'll be able to design campaigns aligned with business goals, allocate budgets across channels, and launch coordinated marketing campaigns across email, messaging, advertising, and other channels.\n\nYou'll also learn how to optimize performance through A/B testing, monitor ROAS and conversions in real time, and manage approvals and permissions securely.",
