    "guideFaqTitle": "Frequently Asked Questions",
    "guideFaq1Q": "Can I run campaigns across multiple channels simultaneously?",
    "guideFaq1A": "Yes. Campaigns can run across email, messaging, advertising, and other connected channels while consolidating performance data into a single dashboard.",
    "guideFaq2Q": "How is ROAS calculated?",
    "guideFaq2A": "ROAS is calculated automatically by dividing campaign-generated revenue by campaign spend.",
    "guideFaq3Q": "How is an A/B test winner selected?",
    "guideFaq3A": "The winning version is selected based on the chosen performance metrics and statistical confidence level.",
    "guideFaq4Q": "Can campaign budgets be changed after launch?",
    "guideFaq4A": "Yes. Budgets can be adjusted and reallocated while campaigns are running.",
    "guideFaq5Q": "Who can approve or launch campaigns?",
    "guideFaq5A": "Only users with the required permissions can approve or launch campaigns. All actions are recorded in audit logs.",
    "guideFaq6Q": "Can CRM segments be used immediately?",
    "guideFaq6A": "Yes. CRM segments can be connected instantly and audience consent can be validated automatically.",
    "guideSecurityTitle": "Security & Privacy",
