    "guideOpsTitle": "Recommended Operational Reviews",
    "guideOpsDesc": "Regular reviews help maintain healthy campaign performance.\n\nDaily Reviews\n• Campaign Status Monitoring\n• Budget Utilization Tracking\n\nWeekly Reviews\n• Channel ROAS Analysis\n• A/B Test Review\n\nMonthly Reviews\n• Campaign Performance Assessment\n• Budget Reallocation Planning\n• Permission Review",
