    "guideStep1Desc": "Choose the external platform or marketplace you want to connect.\n\nSupported Channels\n• Coupang\n• Naver Smart Store\n• Naver Search Ads\n• Meta Ads\n• Google Ads\n• TikTok Business\n• Kakao Moment\n\nResult\nThe recommended authentication method is automatically displayed.",
    "guideStep2Phase": "Phase A · Preparation & Setup",
    "guideStep2Title": "Review Authentication Requirements",
