    "guideStep3Phase": "Phase B · Credential Registration",
    "guideStep3Title": "Add Credentials",
    "guideStep3Desc": "Register authentication credentials using the Add Credential feature.\n\nRequired Information\n• Channel Selection\n• Authentication Method\n• API Key or Access Token\n• Description (Optional)\n\nResult\nCredentials are securely encrypted and stored.",
    "guideStep4Phase": "Phase B · Credential Registration",
