    "guideStep5Phase": "Phase B · Credential Registration",
    "guideStep5Title": "Apply Credentials to Services",
    "guideStep5Desc": "Assign verified credentials to operational features.\n\nUse Cases\n• Order Synchronization\n• Product Synchronization\n• Advertising Data Collection\n• Message Delivery\n\nResult\nExternal channel data begins flowing into the platform.",
    "guideStep6Phase": "Phase C · Operations & Synchronization",
    "guideStep6Title": "Monitor Synchronization Status",
    "guideStep6Desc": "Monitor integration health and synchronization activity across channels.\n\nMetrics\n• Last Sync Time\n• Active/Inactive Status\n• Latest Test Result\n\nResult\nIntegration status is visible at a glance.",
    "guideStep7Phase": "Phase C · Operations & Synchronization",
